---
import NsMonogram from './NsMonogram.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="about-sec">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">About</div>
      <h2 class="sec-title">Between the raw data and the decision.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid reveal">
      <div class="about-portrait" aria-hidden="true">
        <NsMonogram />
        <span class="ap-meta">NS · identity</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>I'm <b>Nico</b> — a data &amp; BI engineer building the after-sales analytics platform at <b>bekumoo</b>. I live in the layer between raw data and the decisions it should drive: orchestrating pipelines, modeling warehouses, and shipping the dashboards people actually open.</p>
        <p>Lately I've been teaching <b>language models to reason over domain data</b> — a retrieval-augmented scouting assistant being the current playground. Solid in SQL, Python, TypeScript and Azure; frontend and React are my deliberate growth edge, and this site is part of that work.</p>
        <p class="placeholder-note">— prototype copy, grounded but placeholder</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-sec {
    padding: 14vh 0;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.15fr;
    gap: 50px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
    }
  }

  .about-grid p {
    color: var(--ink-dim);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-family: var(--mono);
  }

  .about-grid p + p {
    margin-top: 18px;
  }

  .about-grid b {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .placeholder-note {
    color: var(--ink-faint) !important;
    font-size: 13px !important;
  }

  .about-portrait {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    max-width: 240px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background:
      radial-gradient(120% 120% at 30% 20%, rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.10), transparent 60%),
      var(--surface);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }

  /* scanline overlay */
  .about-portrait::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.5;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      0deg,
      transparent 0 2px,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 3px
    );
  }

  /* constrain the NsMonogram SVG inside the portrait box */
  .about-portrait :global(svg) {
    width: 60%;
    height: auto;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  .ap-meta {
    position: absolute;
    left: 12px;
    bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    z-index: 1;
  }
</style>
